children.subject: Thanks for letting us know, hope you all had a wonderful last month :)

history.content:
Our Soda CS advisors, Carol, Charlene, Leslie, & Lydia, have moved into 349 Soda! During this transition, they will not have phone access for a couple of weeks. Please schedule appointments like normal via CalCentral or come to drop-in hours on Wednesday, 10-12PM & 1-4PM. You can also email cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu for quick questions.

Andrea & Nicole will continue to see CS/CS-intended students by appointment only in 205 Cory.
